    <item>
      <title>美国石油供应商切入OPEC+主导的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/us-oil-suppliers-cut-into-markets-dominated-by-opec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自西方国家于 2022 年开始对俄罗斯实施制裁以来，美国石油供应商已强行进入曾经由 OPEC 及其盟友主导的市场，创下了五个新的月度出口记录。安东尼·迪保拉 (Anthony DiPaola) 接受彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/us-oil-suppliers-cut-into-markets-dominated-by-opec</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 10:25:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对派获胜后土耳其建筑公司暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/turkish-construction-firms-tumble-after-opposition-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其执政党在市政选举中遭遇前所未有的失败，导致政府支持的大型项目实现的可能性降低，周一伊斯坦布尔的建筑公司股价大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/turkish-construction-firms-tumble-after-opposition-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 10:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦法院暂停伊姆兰·汗一案的判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/imran-khan-s-sentence-in-one-case-suspended-by-pakistan-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总理伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 因执政期间非法交易国家礼品罪两个月后，巴基斯坦一家法院暂时缓刑了他 14 年的监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/imran-khan-s-sentence-in-one-case-suspended-by-pakistan-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:54:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯计划将4月份柴油海运出口量降至5个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-plans-to-cut-diesel-export-by-sea-in-april-to-5-month-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在乌克兰无人机袭击炼油厂和季节性维护大幅降低原油加工率后，俄罗斯计划将 4 月份西方主要港口的每日柴油出口量降至五个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-plans-to-cut-diesel-export-by-sea-in-april-to-5-month-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险资产出现任何下跌时迅速介入：汇丰银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/jump-in-quickly-to-any-dip-in-risk-assets-hsbc-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰全球研究部首席多资产策略师马克斯·凯特纳(Max Kettner)认为，市场将出现2017年风格的情景，投资者等待下跌，因为美国股市可能“距离现在还有相当大的涨幅”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/jump-in-quickly-to-any-dip-in-risk-assets-hsbc-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:46:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求下滑后巴基斯坦通胀降至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-a-third-month-as-high-rates-hit-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于创纪录的借贷成本削弱了经济增长和国内需求，巴基斯坦3月份的通胀率连续第三个月放缓至近两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-a-third-month-as-high-rates-hit-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对派席卷土耳其地方选举后里拉下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安领导的执政党在周日的地方选举中惨败，包括伊斯坦布尔和安卡拉在内的土耳其许多城市的控制权落入反对派手中，土耳其里拉走弱。信用违约掉期有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 05:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乐观的 PMI 数据增强了复苏希望，中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/chinese-stocks-gain-as-upbeat-pmi-data-reinforce-recovery-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于制造业活动反弹增强了人们对中国经济复苏可能开始获得动力的希望，中国股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/chinese-stocks-gain-as-upbeat-pmi-data-reinforce-recovery-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商考虑脆弱的中国复苏，铁矿石价格波动近 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iron-ore-sinks-to-10-month-low-on-gloom-over-china-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对该国经济复苏可能开始增强的乐观情绪抵消了钢铁市场的疲软，铁矿石价格在跌至 10 个月以来的最低水平后逆转了方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iron-ore-sinks-to-10-month-low-on-gloom-over-china-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
